data.description: Welcome to this stunning, meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. The kitchen great features, boasting elegant granite countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and soft-close drawers. The living room is bathed in natural light, featuring a vaulted ceiling with a charming beam accent and a cozy gas fireplace, creating the perfect space for relaxation and entertaining.  Step outside to discover the enchanting backyard, complete with a flourishing young oak tree and a spacious deck, offering an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the beauty of nature. This home truly embodies the perfect blend of comfort, style, and tranquility.
